actions.text: Measure called up by unanimous consent in Senate.

official_title: A resolution relative to the death of Honorable Hubert H. Humphrey, a former Vice President of the United States and a late Senator from the State of Minnesota.

summary.text: Expresses the condolences of the Senate upon the death of the Honorable Hubert H. Humphrey, former Vice President of the United States and a Senator from the State of Minnesota.

titles.title: A resolution relative to the death of Honorable Hubert H. Humphrey, a former Vice President of the United States and a late Senator from the State of Minnesota.
